      • requiresCookies

        boolean requiresCookies()
        Returns if this authentication method requires cookies. Implementations should take following into account:
        • the authentication method (some methods require cookies to work)
        • the binding and its cookie setting
        • the CSRF settings
        Returns:
        true if cookies are required, false if cookies are not required (they may be recommended, though)
